{"tid":219564,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蓋 表演飲「屎水」：日日飲都得","createTime":"2017-04-27T10:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T05:13:28.000Z","uid":3806,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"093d402b9d36485be54aa36a8d3e44d4ef208675","tid":219564,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20150108/large/08ww6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20150108%2Flarge%2F08ww6p.jpg&h=d7b36b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微軟創辦人蓋茨（Bill Gates）繼去年「淋冰水」挑戰之後，新年再表演「飲屎水」！<br />\n他名下的慈善基金會資助美國生化能源公司Janicki生產「全能處理器」（Omniprocessor），更在鏡頭前喝掉淨化過的「屎水」（圖）。處理器以1,000℃高溫將糞便煮沸分化，蒸氣濾成無色無臭的食水，燒過的污物就作發電燃料。<br />\n蓋茨在網誌寫道：「看着一堆糞便沿輸送帶掉進大桶裏，由機器煮沸處理，幾分鐘後就喝到完成品：一杯美味的食水&hellip;&hellip;我可以天天喝，十分安全。」<br />\n蓋茨表示全球仍有20億人面對衞生及食水污染問題，全能處理器一舉兩得，一台約150萬美金（1,770萬港元），可淨化10萬人社區的排泄物。<br />\n中央社/英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"ea92d8a0394e1d49f91b512c46bc135ced51a1b7","tid":219564,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"卡牢好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4383d4fd191ee69b30bde3ccdaf585e35b78acc5","tid":219564,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卡牢好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e0c59f771654e8f13945c8ac47f25835b98bc3","tid":219564,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卡牢好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無屎水圖？link 死哂"},{"pid":"cc119fd9938946f439fc61d35faa75e9204d5624","tid":219564,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:14:48.000